source.name: U.S. Census Bureau - 2020 ZCTA5 to 2020 Place relationship file

notes: This file contains Census 'Places' (municipalities) and Census ZCTAs that intersect each place.
A ZCTA can overlap multiple places; the same ZCTA may appear in multiple municipalities.
land_part_m2 is the land overlap area between the place and ZCTA for that row.
